t: Electrothermal
s: Electrothermal is an Essex-based company which was founded in 1941. The company has become a specialist in precisely controlled heating and cooling applications. The Electrothermal brand is now part of the Bibby Scientific group, which also incorporates Jenway, Stuart and Techne.
